## Type Declarations

- All PHP files must use `declare(strict_types=1);`
- Method parameters and return values must have type declarations

Reference: `app/Http/Controllers/TodoController.php`

## Model Standards

- Define $fillable attributes
- Use $casts for type conversion
- Use Laravel Enums for enum fields

Reference: `app/Models/Todo.php`

## Controller Standards

- Use authentication middleware to protect routes requiring login
- Implement user data isolation (users can only operate on their own data)
- Use FormRequest for data validation
- Return Inertia responses for frontend rendering

Reference: `app/Http/Controllers/TodoController.php`

## Data Transfer Objects (DTOs)

- Use Spatie Laravel Data package
- Add TypeScript transformation annotations

Reference: `app/Data/TodoData.php`

## Request Validation

- Use FormRequest classes for validation
- Check permissions in authorize method
- Use Laravel enums for validation

